ZH: 依循传统习俗，我们会在农历新年赠送红包。
EN: Following tradition, we will gift red packets during the Lunar New Year.

ZH: 他们依循公司政策，每年都要参加培训课程。
EN: They follow the company policy and attend training courses every year.

ZH: 我们应该依循规定的路线前进，不要轻易偏离。
EN: We should follow the prescribed route and not deviate easily.

ZH: 警察依循法律程序，逮捕了犯罪嫌疑人。
EN: The police followed legal procedures and arrested the criminal suspect.

ZH: 这个项目依循严格的时间表进行，确保按时完成。
EN: This project follows a strict schedule to ensure completion on time.

ZH: 在工作中，我始终依循自己的原则。
EN: In my work, I always adhere to my own principles.

ZH: 学生们应该依循教师的指导来完成作业。
EN: Students should follow the teacher's guidance to complete the assignment.

