EN: Athletes follow a strict training plan to improve physical fitness.

ZH: 公司员工都是依循公司价值观的。
EN: Company employees all adhere to the company's values.

ZH: 军事行动必须依循军事指挥部的命令。
EN: Military operations must follow the orders of the military command.

