EN: We should follow the light signals to ensure smooth traffic flow.

ZH: 组织的发展与改革须依循正确的方向。
EN: The development and reform of an organization must follow the right direction.

ZH: 做事要有计划，不要随意依循情绪。
EN: When doing things, have a plan and don't follow emotions randomly.

